Title: GTEx_v6_junctions_fibroblast
Description: data.frame containing counts for all junctions originating from GTEx v6 fibroblast samples.Each row corresponds to a junction. Columns detail the 'chr', 'start', 'end', 'strand' and remaining columns refer to each GTEx sample in the format 'gtex_XXXXX', XXXXX being the rail_id from snaptron.Data has been released via the recount2 project, downloaded by snaptron and wrangled into convienient format for use in the dasper package.
